  <div class="content">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to <strong>The Online Book Library</strong>your virtual haven for exploring and enjoying books anytime, anywhere. Whether you enjoy reading, require books for school, or simply wish to discover new tales, our library offers something for all!</p>
    
    <h2>Our Objective</h2>
    <p>At <strong>The Online Book Library</strong>,our goal is to make reading enjoyable and accessible for all. We think books are an excellent means to learn, develop, and appreciate stories, which is why we offer a diverse range of books online for free or at an affordable price.</p>

    <h2>What We Provide</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Extensive Book Selection:</strong>Our inventory includes thousands of titles, ranging from timeless classics to current bestsellers, encompassing a wide variety of genres such as fiction, non-fiction, fantasy, history, and beyond. </li>
      <li><strong>Use Friendly:</strong> Our site is easy to explore, allowing you to search by title, author, or genre. We additionally recommend books according to your preferences.</li>
      <li><strong>Anytime, Anywhere Access:</strong> No matter if you’re at home, in class, or traveling, you can read our books on your phone, tablet, or computer—around the clock.</li>
      <li><strong>Personal Recommendations:</strong> Get suggestions for books based on your preferences and interests.</li>
      <li><strong>Reader Community:</strong>Exchange reviews, score books, and engage with fellow readers who adore the same stories as you.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Convenience:</strong>There’s no need to go to a library or wait for a book's delivery. You can instantly borrow and read.</li>
      <li><strong>Budget-friendly:</strong> Numerous books are available for free, and the others are provided at reasonable prices. No concealed charges!</li>
      <li><strong>Varied Range:</strong>Our publications feature writers from across the globe, offering you an opportunity to experience various cultures and concepts.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Join Us</h2>
    <p>Register today to discover countless books and join our expanding reading community.</p>

    <p><em>Happy Reading!</em><br>
